metadata.name: Tokyu REIT Inc
metadata.description: TOKYU REIT, Inc. was incorporated to invest in real estate on June 20, 2003 under the Law Concerning Investment Trusts and Investment Corporations of Japan (Law No. 198 of 1952, as amended), or the Investment Trust Law. Such corporations are commonly referred to as Japanese Real Estate Investment Trusts, or J-REITs.
